Origin and attribution

The pricing-catalog model, the per-token cost arithmetic, the tier and
capability selection primitives, the cross-provider fallback ordering, the
retryable-error classification, and the MCP packaging pattern in this project
were derived from prior internal Workswarm software. That internal software was
re-expressed here as dependency-free, framework-free functions for this
open-source release; the published bundle incorporates no third-party code and
carries no third-party license obligation.

The bundled pricing catalog (catalog.json) reflects published provider list
prices as of the dates recorded in its asOf fields and per-entry source URLs.
Those prices are the property of the respective model providers and are included
for cost-estimation reference only; they carry no warranty of accuracy or
currency. Verify against each provider's pricing page before relying on a figure
for billing.
